What you need to know:  Pep Guardiola's men will claim a fourth English title in five years of a dominant era for Abu Dhabi-backed City with victory over Aston Villa.Gerrard famously never won a league title in his 17-year career at Anfield, but could deliver one on a plate to his old club.Jurgen Klopp's men have already lifted the League Cup and FA Cup.